	{\check{a}} & c & 0
	\arrow["{\alpha^\ell}", from=1-1, to=1-2]
	\arrow[from=2-1, to=2-2]
	\arrow["{\mathrm{d}_v^{0, \ell -1 }}"', from=2-2, to=1-2]
	\arrow["{\mathrm{d}_h^{0, \ell - 1}}", from=2-2, to=2-3]
\end{tikzcd}\]
And since everything commutes $\alpha^\ell(\delta^{\ell - 1}(\check{a})) = \alpha^\ell(a)$, which by
